text: Salon Basnet is a Nepali actor and model. He started his career in Nepali Film Industry as a child actor from the movie “Nepali Babu”. He rose to fame from superhit Nepali Movies “Hostel” & “Gajalu”. He is listed as one of the top actors of Nepal. ==Filmography== * ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Kathmandu Category:Nepalese models
